  hindiTitle `मुस्लिम विवाह विघटन अधिनियम, 1939`
  actYear (1939)
  ministry `Ministry of Law and Justice`
  department `Legislative Department`
  longTitle `An Act to consolidate and clarify the provisions of Muslim law relating to suits for dissolution of marriage by women married under Muslim law and to remove doubts as to the effect of the renunciation of Islam by a married Muslim woman on her marriage tie.`
  enforcementDate 17-03-1939
